channel.title: Welcome to our newest janitor, Dadmother!
channel.description:
Some of you noticed already that @Dadmother has been granted the leader role, but he's also been switched over to full janitorial duties. Dadmo is a great member of the community, super supportive and is excited to lend a hand.
Give him a warm welcome and super dad(mom) high fives :raised_hands:t2:
